82
00:04:33.460 --> 00:04:35.210
Alcohol Soft?

83
00:04:35.210 --> 00:04:36.750
Never heard of them.

84
00:04:36.750 --> 00:04:38.450
I'm not familiar with them.

85
00:04:42.170 --> 00:04:45.880
<i>I've checked a bunch of 
stores, but zero leads.</i>

86
00:04:45.880 --> 00:04:48.820
<i>Maybe it was all in my head,</i>

87
00:04:48.820 --> 00:04:50.830
<i>because I wanted to make a game so badly.</i>

88
